# Problem
In order to deal with a higher variety of situations pertaining changes in the number of drones and sensors, we are going to try a strategy of using a sequential model (perhaps Transformer based). The idea is reading observations a a sequence of sensor and drone information. Sequences can have variable size; thus, our model will be able to perform no matter the number of drones and sensors.

# Solution
I have modified the environment to produce a sequence of positions for the drone and sensor part of the observation. For now the sequences are flattened and the existing model is used. We want to validate that performance doesn't change compared to **variable_sensor**, meaning our implementation is correct

# Results
No performance change observed. The implementation is working